com.mia.umlmia.behavioralelements.statemachines
Interface UMLState

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAEvaluableObject, com.mia.openapi.MIAObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, UMLMIAObject, UMLModelElement, UMLState, UMLStateVertex
All Known Subinterfaces:
UMLActionState, UMLCallState, UMLCompositeState, UMLFinalState, UMLObjectFlowState, UMLSimpleState, UMLSubactivityState, UMLSubmachineState
public interface UMLState
extends UMLStateVertex, UMLState

A representation of the model object 'UML State'.

The following features are supported:

  • Do Activity
  • Entry
  • Exit
  • State Machine
  • Deferrable Events
  • Internals

See Also:
